    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm going to close this, as in the latest version of the spec validators are allowed to sign multiple blocks per epoch, just not _per slot_. The code for storing the `slots_per_epoch` in the slashing database has been removed, and I think limiting the slashing protection to do just what is required for security helps keep the code clean.",
